<li><a href="http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/14.07/posts.html?pg=5" class="external text" title="http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/14.07/posts.html?pg=5" rel="nofollow">Meet the Geek Elite</a>, <a href="/wiki/Wired_Magazine" title="Wired Magazine" class="mw-redirect">Wired Magazine</a>, July 2006</li>
